        <h1 class="w-display lr-hero__h">What is the Trust Layer for B2B Sales?</h1>
        <p class="lr-hero__sub">Buyers stopped taking the vendor's word and started taking each other's. The Trust Layer gets a real customer's proof to the right buyer at the moment it decides the deal — both when they come looking and before they ever ask.</p>
        <div class="lr-hero__actions">
          <a class="w-btn w-btn--primary w-btn--lg" href="/book-a-demo">Book a Demo <svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></a>
