          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lr-arrow w-reveal" aria-hidden="true"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-arrow-right"/></svg></div>
        <div class="w-card w-card--brand lr-fcard w-reveal w-reveal--scale">
          <span class="w-card__icon lr-fcard__ic"><svg class="w-icon"><use href="#i-megaphone"/></svg></span>
          <h3 class="w-card__title">It delivers at the deciding moment.</h3>
          <p class="w-card__body">It puts that proof in front of the buyer when it counts — the instant they come looking, and proactively when a deal is ready and no one has asked yet.</p>
          <div class="lr-fcard__viz lrv lrv3" aria-hidden="true">
            <div class="lrv-row"><span class="lrv-dot"></span><span class="lrv-tx"><b>Deal &middot; Evaluation</b><small>Buyer comparing options</small></span></div>
